                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18080217-6-off29 t18080217-6-cd30"></join>, three pair of cotton stockings, value 3 s. three pair of silk stockings, value 1 l. seven shirts, value 30 s. a pair of trowsers, value 5 s. three waistcoats, value 15 s. two pair of breeches, value 2 l. three sheets, value 30 s. three table cloths, value 3 l. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18080217-6-victim98" type="victimName">
